    "• Selective Coding: These sub-themes were then integrated into overarching themes, forming the basis of our findings.An analytical framework was adopted to organize themes within the broader context of AI's role in promoting sustainability and ethical standards in higher education.",
    "This framework guided the synthesis of findings across studies and is presented in the following section.",
    "Ethical considerationsRecognizing the sensitivity of educational data, we prioritized studies addressing privacy, algorithmic bias, and the digital divide [53].",
